<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>We Miss You</title>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .content h2 { color: #333333; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .content p { color: #666666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; }
        .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; }
        .news-box { background-color: #e8f5e9; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; }
        .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: #999999; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer a { color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸ‘‹ We Miss You, <%= name %>!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>It's been <%= daysInactive %> days...</h2>
            
            <p>We noticed you haven't been active on Engagematic lately, and we wanted to check in!</p>
            
            <p>Your LinkedIn presence doesn't have to take a backseat. We're here to make content creation effortless.</p>
            
            <div class="news-box">
                <strong style="color: #2e7d32; font-size: 18px;">What's New Since You've Been Away:</strong>
                <ul style="color: #2e7d32; line-height: 1.8; margin: 15px 0 0 0;">
                    <li>Enhanced AI for even better content quality</li>
                    <li>New viral hook templates added</li>
                    <li>Improved analytics dashboard</li>
                    <li>Faster content generation</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>Quick Win:</strong> Create a post in 60 seconds:</p>
            <ol style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Pick a topic you're passionate about</li>
                <li>Choose a hook from our library</li>
                <li>Let AI craft your perfect post</li>
                <li>Publish and watch the engagement roll in</li>
            </ol>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%=  %>/dashboard" class="cta-button">
                    Jump Back In â†’
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <% if (daysInactive >= 30) { %>
            <div style="background-color: #fff3e0; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <strong style="color: #e65100;">Welcome Back Gift:</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #e65100;">Log in within 7 days and get 50 bonus AI tokens + exclusive access to our new features!</p>
            </div>
            <% } %>
            
            <p><strong>Need help getting back on track?</strong> We're here for you! Reply to this email and let us know what we can do to help.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Your LinkedIn success is waiting,<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> | 
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

